nal Brand Area (Vietnam Value) – Industrial Products Zone – Real Zone Consumer products. Especially, at Vietnam Expo this year, there will be the latest products and technologies in the impressive and elaborately designed pavilions.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '202-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-06-22 22:04:43', '2019-06-22 15:04:43', '', 202, 'http://elevator_vnexpo.co/202-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
