(241, 1, '2019-06-23 01:06:19', '2019-06-22 18:06:19', '<div id="pl-8"  class="panel-layout" ><div id="pg-8-0"  class="panel-grid panel-has-style"  data-style="{&quot;class&quot;:&quot;introduce_index&quot;,&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;cell_alignment&quot;:&quot;flex-start&quot;}"  data-ratio="1"  data-ratio-direction="right" ><div class="introduce_index panel-row-style panel-row-style-for-8-0" ><div id="pgc-8-0-0"  class="panel-grid-cell"  data-weight="1" ><div id="panel-8-0-0-0" class="so-panel widget widget_black-studio-tinymce widget_black_studio_tinymce panel-first-child panel-last-child" data-index="0" data-style="{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}" ><h3 class="widget-title">WELCOME TO LIFTEX 2019</h3><div class="textwidget">LIFTEX 2019 took place from the 15-16 May 2019 at ExCeL London, it is the only dedicated exhibition for the lift, escalator and access industry to be held in the UK.\n\nOrganised by the Lift and Escalator Industry Association (LEIA) and held every three years, it featured 120 UK &amp; international exhibitors showcasing the latest products and services from around the world.</div></div></div></div></div></div>', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '8-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-06-23 01:06:19', '2019-06-22 18:06:19', '', 8, 'http://elevator_vnexpo.co/8-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(274, 1, '2019-06-23 15:34:32', '2019-06-23 08:34:32', '<div id="pl-84"  class="panel-layout" ><div id="pg-84-0"  class="panel-grid panel-no-style"  data-style="{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;cell_alignment&quot;:&quot;flex-start&quot;}"  data-ratio="1"  data-ratio-direction="right" ><div id="pgc-84-0-0"  class="panel-grid-cell"  data-weight="1" ><div id="panel-84-0-0-0" class="so-panel widget widget_black-studio-tinymce widget_black_studio_tinymce panel-first-child panel-last-child" data-index="0" data-style="{&quot;class&quot;:&quot;ul_check  why_exhybit&quot;,&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}" ><div class="ul_check  why_exhybit panel-widget-style panel-widget-style-for-84-0-0-0" ><div class="textwidget">Không có sự kiện nào khác tập hợp nhiều người ra quyết định quan trọng trong khoảng thời gian hai ngày. Hơn 2.700 khách tham quan với sức mua thực sự đã tham dự triển lãm, tất cả đều mong muốn được gặp gỡ các nhà cung cấp mới, tìm kiếm sản phẩm mới, mạng lưới và hình thành các mối quan hệ kinh doanh mới.\n</div></div></div></div></div><div id="pg-84-1"  class="panel-grid panel-no-style"  data-style="{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;cell_alignment&quot;:&quot;flex-start&quot;}" ><div id="pgc-84-1-0"  class="panel-grid-cell"  data-weight="0.5" ><div id="panel-84-1-0-0" class="so-panel widget widget_black-studio-tinymce widget_black_studio_tinymce panel-first-child panel-last-child" data-index="1" data-style="{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}" ><div class="textwidget"><ul class="ul_check">\n 	<li>Chỉ có thị trường dành riêng cho LIFT, Thang cuốn &amp; Công nghiệp truy cập ở Anh</li>\n 	<li>Đây là sự kiện trong ngành của bạn được thiết kế để giúp bạn tạo doanh nghiệp của mình trong 3 năm tới</li>\n 	<li>Cơ hội gặp gỡ 665 triệu doanh nghiệp tiềm năng chỉ sau hai ngày</li>\n 	<li>Cung cấp cho hàng ngàn người ra quyết định cấp cao đang có mặt để mua</li>\n</ul></div></div></div><div id="pgc-84-1-1"  class="panel-grid-cell"  data-weight="0.5" ><div id="panel-84-1-1-0" class="so-panel widget widget_black-studio-tinymce widget_black_studio_tinymce panel-first-child panel-last-child" data-index="2" data-style="{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}" ><div class="textwidget"><ul class="ul_check">\n 	<li>Được tổ chức và vận hành bởi LEIA (Hiệp hội công nghiệp thang máy và thang cuốn)</li>\n 	<li>Chỉ được tổ chức ba năm một lần</li>\n 	<li>Được hỗ trợ bởi hơn 100 nhà triển lãm Vương quốc Anh và quốc tế</li>\n 	<li>Kết nối với các đồng nghiệp Vương quốc Anh và toàn cầu</li>\n</ul></div></div></div></div></div>', 'Why exhibit', 'No other event gathers many important decision makers over a two-day period. More than 2,700 visitors with real purchasing power attended the exhibition, all looking forward to meeting new suppliers, finding new products, networks and forming new business relationships.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '84-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-06-23 15:34:32', '2019-06-23 08:34:32', '', 84, 'http://elevator_vnexpo.co/84-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(275, 1, '2019-06-23 15:36:15', '2019-06-23 08:36:15', '<div id="pl-84"  class="panel-layout" ><div id="pg-84-0"  class="panel-grid panel-no-style"  data-style="{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;cell_alignment&quot;:&quot;flex-start&quot;}"  data-ratio="1"  data-ratio-direction="right" ><div id="pgc-84-0-0"  class="panel-grid-cell"  data-weight="1" ><div id="panel-84-0-0-0" class="so-panel widget widget_black-studio-tinymce widget_black_studio_tinymce panel-first-child panel-last-child" data-index="0" data-style="{&quot;class&quot;:&quot;ul_check  why_exhybit&quot;,&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}" ><div class="ul_check  why_exhybit panel-widget-style panel-widget-style-for-84-0-0-0" ><div class="textwidget">No other event gathers many important decision makers over a two-day period. More than 2,700 visitors with real purchasing power attended the exhibition, all looking forward to meeting new suppliers, finding new products, networks and forming new business relationships.</div></div></div></div></div><div id="pg-84-1"  class="panel-grid panel-no-style"  data-style="{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;cell_alignment&quot;:&quot;flex-start&quot;}" ><div id="pgc-84-1-0"  class="panel-grid-cell"  data-weight="0.5" ><div id="panel-84-1-0-0" class="so-panel widget widget_black-studio-tinymce widget_black_studio_tinymce panel-first-child panel-last-child" data-index="1" data-style="{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}" ><div class="textwidget"><ul class="ul_check">\n 	<li>Only dedicated market place for the LIFT, Escalator &amp; Access Industry in the UK</li>\n 	<li>It is your industry event designed to help you generate business for the next 3 years</li>\n 	<li>Opportunity to meet £665m of potential business in just two days*</li>\n 	<li>Delivers thousands of senior decision-making visitors who are there to buy</li>\n</ul></div></div></div><div id="pgc-84-1-1"  class="panel-grid-cell"  data-weight="0.5" ><div id="panel-84-1-1-0" class="so-panel widget widget_black-studio-tinymce widget_black_studio_tinymce panel-first-child panel-last-child" data-index="2" data-style="{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}" ><div class="textwidget"><ul class="ul_check">\n 	<li>Organised and run by LEIA (Lift and Escalator Industry Association)</li>\n 	<li>Staged only once every three years</li>\n 	<li>Supported by over 100 UK &amp; international exhibitors</li>\n 	<li>Network with your UK and global peers</li>\n</ul></div></div></div></div></div>', 'Why exhibit', 'No other event gathers many important decision makers over a two-day period. More than 2,700 visitors with real purchasing power attended the exhibition, all looking forward to meeting new suppliers, finding new products, networks and forming new business relationships.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '84-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-06-23 15:36:15', '2019-06-23 08:36:15', '', 84, 'http://elevator_vnexpo.co/84-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
