(434, 1, '2019-07-03 21:25:09', '2019-07-03 14:25:09', '<div id="pl-84"  class="panel-layout" ><div id="pg-84-0"  class="panel-grid panel-no-style"  data-style="{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;cell_alignment&quot;:&quot;flex-start&quot;}"  data-ratio="1"  data-ratio-direction="right" ><div id="pgc-84-0-0"  class="panel-grid-cell"  data-weight="1" ><div id="panel-84-0-0-0" class="so-panel widget widget_black-studio-tinymce widget_black_studio_tinymce panel-first-child panel-last-child" data-index="0" data-style="{&quot;class&quot;:&quot;ul_check  why_exhybit&quot;,&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}" ><div class="ul_check  why_exhybit panel-widget-style panel-widget-style-for-84-0-0-0" ><div class="textwidget">No other event brings together so many key decision makers across a two-day period. Over 2,000 visitors with real purchasing power attended the show, all looking to meet new suppliers, find new products, network and form new business relationships.\n\nThis is an important event in the first elevator industry held in Vietnam.\n\nThe chance to meet trade takes place during the three days of the exhibition.\n\nDelivers thousands of senior decision-making visitors who are there to buy.\n\nNetwork with your Vietnam and global peers.\n\n&nbsp;</div></div></div></div></div><div id="pg-84-1"  class="panel-grid panel-no-style"  data-style="{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;cell_alignment&quot;:&quot;flex-start&quot;}" ><div id="pgc-84-1-0"  class="panel-grid-cell"  data-weight="0.5" ><div id="panel-84-1-0-0" class="so-panel widget widget_black-studio-tinymce widget_black_studio_tinymce panel-first-child panel-last-child" data-index="1" data-style="{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}" ><div class="textwidget"><ul class="