c tổ chức bởi Công ty Vinexad (Bộ Công Thương) với 43 năm kinh nghiệm trong tổ chức các hoạt động xúc tiến thương mại. Với bề dày kinh nghiệm và nguồn dữ liệu khách hàng phong phú, mục tiêu của khách tham gia là cơ sở để ban tổ chức không ngừng cung cấp những dịch vụ tốt nhất.\r\n\r\nTriển lãm sẽ mở cửa trong 4 ngày, từ 9h sáng đến 5h chiều và dự kiến sẽ đón tiếp khoảng 15,000 lượt khách tới tham quan và làm việc.', 'Giới thiệu', 'Triển lãm Quốc tế chuyên ngành Thực phẩm – Đồ uống & Thiết bị Công nghệ chế biến, bao bì thực phẩm và đồ uống với tên gọi Vietfood & Beverage -  ProPack là triển lãm đầu tiên và duy nhất tại Việt Nam được tổ chức từ năm 1996 đến nay. Triển lãm đã tổ chức thành công 23 kỳ tại Tp. Hồ Chí Minh (tháng 8 hàng năm) và đang từng bước gây dựng mô hình này tại Tp. Hà Nội (tháng 11). Với mục tiêu rõ ràng trong khâu tổ chức từ kết nối xúc tiến thương mại giữa các doanh nghiệp trong và ngoài nước (B2B) cho đến các hoạt động quảng cáo bán lẻ (B2C), Vietfood Beverage – ProPack 2019 sẽ tiếp tục quay trở lại từ ngày 6-9/11 tại Trung tâm triển lãm ICE – 91 Trần Hưng Đạo, Q. Hoàn Kiếm, Tp. Hà Nội do Công ty Vinexad thực hiện cùng phối hợp với các tổ chức xúc tiến các nước và các Hiệp hội ngành hàng liên quan.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '58-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-09-07 23:27:36', '2019-09-07 16:27:36', '', 58, 'http://vietfood.co/58-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(610, 1, '2019-09-07 23:29:32', '2019-09-07 16:29:32', '<strong>ONGOING SUCCESS</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>VIETFOOD &amp; BEVERAGE – PROPACK 2019</strong> is organised from <strong>6<sup>th</sup> – 9<sup>th</sup> November at Hanoi International Exhibition Center – 91 Tran Hung Dao Str., Hoan Kiem District, Hanoi.</strong>\r\n\r\nVegetables (fresh, dried, canned, ready made); aqua products (processed, canned); agricultural products (coffee, tea, chestnuts, pepper); materials for food-beverage-bakery process; alcohol drinks, tea, coffee, food packaging equipment; franchising brands; equipment and accessories for restaurants and hotels.\r\n\r\n<img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-607" src="http://vietfood.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/gioithieu-600x400.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="400" />\r\n\r\n<strong>LOCAL AND INTERNATIONAL BRANDS COME TOGETHER</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>VIETFOOD &amp; BEVERAGE – PROPACK 2019 in Hanoi</strong> manifests the return of local brands such as Cánh Đồng Vàng (Golden Farm), Minh Tiến Coffee, Sen Việt Company, Chính Sơn’s Tea, Minh Trung’s Food, Bến Tre Imports and Exports Company, Thực phẩm Xanh (Organic Food) who will present outstanding products made by local such as tea, fruit juice, dried fruit which are popular and consumed by local residents with hope to meet with foreign partners and take local products to farther markets.\r\n\r\n<em>Especially, organic food presented by start-up businesses such as SkyFarm (Gotula); Cầu Đất Farm  with vegetables, tomato, radish, carrot, banana, tea and coffee which all are certified by Global G.A.P. These products will be a spotlight to local consumers.</em>\r\n\r\nParticipated in HoChiMinh City events for several times and recorded achievements, Korean Trade Promotion Center for Forestry and Agricultural Products will join Hanoi event with hope to expand business in the city. The exhibition calls for participations of 33 Korean well-known companies producing products such as <em>ginseng and ginseng products, ganoderma, confectionary, beverage, fruit juice, milk and milk products, fresh and dried fruit, ready food, seaweed, soup, ingredients</em>...\r\n\r\nThis year exhibition calls for participations of <strong>200 businesses</strong> with <strong>250 displays</strong> from <strong>11 nations</strong> and <strong>territories</strong> such as Korea, Thailand, Russia, Malaysia, Italy, Denmark, Spain, Lithuania and China.\r\n\r\n<strong>VIETFOOD &amp; BEVERAGE - PROPACK 2019 IN HANOI</strong> is organized by Vinexad (under Ministry of Industry and Trade) with strong supports of local authorities such as Ministry of Industry and Trade, Ministry of Agriculture and Rural Development, Local and Foreign Associations of Beverages, HoChiMinh City Food Association.\r\n\r\nWe expect to welcome 15,000 arrivals of customers during four day exhibition.', 'Overview', 'VIETFOOD & BEVERAGE – PROPACK 2019 is organised from 6th – 9th November at Hanoi International Exhibition Center – 91 Tran Hung Dao Str., Hoan Kiem District, Hanoi.\r\nVegetables (fresh, dried, canned, ready made); aqua products (processed, canned); agricultural products (coffee, tea, chestnuts, pepper); materials for food-beverage-bakery process; alcohol drinks, tea, coffee, food packaging equipment; franchising brands; equipment and accessories for restaurants and hotels.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '64-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-09-07 23:29:32', '2019-09-07 16:29:32', '', 64, 'http://vietfood.co/64-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(613, 1, '2019-09-08 00:43:51', '2019-09-07 17:43:51', '<div id="pl-112"  class="panel-layout" ><div id="pg-112-0"  class="panel-grid panel-has-style"  data-style="{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;khusp&quot;,&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;cell_alignment&quot;:&quot;flex-start&quot;}"  data-ratio="1"  data-ratio-direction="right" ><div id="khusp" class="panel-row-style panel-row-style-for-112-0" ><div id="pgc-112-0-0"  class="panel-grid-cell"  data-weight="1" ><div id="panel-112-0-0-0" class="so-panel widget widget_siteorigin-panels-builder panel-first-child panel-last-child" data-index="0" data-style="{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}" ><div id="pl-w5d201cce1f794"  class="panel-layout" ><div id="pg-w5d201cce1f794-0"  class="panel-grid panel-no-style"  data-style="{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;cell_alignment&quot;:&quot;flex-start&quot;}"  data-ratio="1"  data-ratio-direction="right" ><div id="pgc-w5d201cce1f794-0-0"  class="panel-grid-cell"  data-weight="1" ><div id="panel-w5d201cce1f794-0-0-0" class="so-panel widget widget_black-studio-tinymce widget_black_studio_tinymce panel-first-child panel-last-child" data-index="0" data-style="{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}" ><div class="textwidget">Vietnam Elevator Expo 2020 được chia thành các loại sản phẩm dành riêng.\n\nTriển lãm về ngành công nghiệp thang máy lần đầu tiên được tổ chức tại Việt Nam có thể cung cấp một số lượng lớn các nhà triển lãm chất lượng và đa dạng nhằm trưng bày các khu vực sản phẩm được xác định dưới đây:</div></div></div></div><div id="pg-w5d201cce1f794-1"  class="panel-grid panel-no-style"  data-style="{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;cell_alignment&quot;:&quot;flex-start&quot;