(702, 1, '2019-09-29 12:00:03', '2019-09-29 05:00:03', '<img class=" wp-image-712 aligncenter" src="http://hn.medipharm.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/medical.png" alt="" width="199" height="128" />\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18pt; color: #1ca1c9;"><strong>VIETNAM  INTERNATIONAL EXHIBITION ON MEDICAL &amp; LABORATORY EQUIPMENT</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #0000ff;">From 06th - 08th August 2020</span>\r\n<span style="color: #0000ff;"><strong>Venue: Saigon Exhibition &amp; Convention Center (SECC) 799 Nguyen van Linh Str., Dist. 7, Ho Chi Minh City, Vietnam</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #0000ff;">From 03rd - 05th December 2020</span>\r\n<span style="color: #0000ff;"><strong>Venue: Hanoi International Center for Exhibition (ICE) - 91 Tran Hung Dao Str., Hanoi, Vietnam</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Product category:</strong></h2>\r\n<strong>Electromedical equipment / Medical technology</strong>\r\n\r\nDiagnostics, Imaging supplies, Surgery devices, endoscopy devices, Therapy and physical medicine, Implants and protheses, Intense medicine / anesthesiology / respiration, Emergency medicine, rescue equipment, Operating technology and operating equipment, Hospital equipment, care equipment, Hygiene / sterilisation / disinfection, Other equipment for electromedicine / medical technology.\r\n\r\n<strong>Laboratory Technology</strong>\r\n\r\nAnalyser systems / equipment,Centrifuges, Chromatographs, Cleaning equipment for laboratory, Drying equipment for laboratory, Filtration systems, filtration equipment, Glass, plastic, metal laboratory items, Homogenizers, Laboratory equipment, Laboratory furniture, Laboratory refrigerators and freezing systems, Laboratory water purification systems, Microplate, microtiter plates, Microscopes, Photometers, Pipetting devices, pipetting equipment, Sampling systems, Scales and balances, Shaking and mixing units, Slide stainers, Spectrometers, Temperature measurement devices, Other laboratory equipment.\r\n\r\n<strong>Diagnostics</strong>\r\n\r\nClinical chemistry, Immunochemistry testing, immunology testing, Haematology / histology / cytology testing, Microbiology testing, Infectious immunology testing, Genetic testing, molecular diagnostics, Other diagnostics.\r\n\r\n<strong>Physiotherapy / Orthopaedic technology</strong>\r\n\r\nHydrotherapy treatment equipment, Bandages in physiotherapy / orthopaedic technology, Occupational therapy equipment, Walking and mobility aids, Compression therapy equipment, Orthopaedic shock wave therapy equipment, Physiotherapeutic mobility aids, Physiotherapy equipment, Physiotherapeutic cold treatment, Physiotherapeutic heat treatment, Physiotherapeutic massage equipment, Rehabilitation equipment and devices, Orthopaedic feet aids, shoes and insoles, Training equipment, Lateral training devices, rehabilitation equipment and devices, Wheelchairs, Other equipment and devices for physiotherapy and orthopaedy.\r\n\r\n<strong>Commodities and consumer goods</strong>\r\n\r\nUniversal medical commodities, Acupuncture equipment and accessories, Articles for nursing, hygiene and medical cosmetic, Batteries for medical systems, Surface disinfectants, Hand hygiene stations / supplies, Disposables, Hearing aids, Incontinence systems and stoma aids, Catheters / urinary catheters and accessories, Sterile bags, Linen, Patient identification wristbands, devices, Personal protective equipment, Wound care equipment, Waste Management, Other commodities and consumer goods.\r\n\r\n<strong>Information technology and communication technology</strong>\r\n\r\nIT infrastructure / computer hardware, mHealth, mobile IT, wireless technologies (Bluetooth, WI-FI), Wearable technologies, smart textiles, eHealth, telemedicine / telematics / telemetry, Administrative information systems / software, Medical information systems / software, Communication systems, Other equipment and d