(710, 1, '2019-09-28 09:58:48', '2019-09-28 02:58:48', 'Vietnam Medipharm Expo is known as one of the leading medical and pharmaceutical exhibitions in Vietnam. Vietnam Medi-Pharm Expo is the best place where the international and domestic enterprises introduce new achievements, machinery, technology and science.\r\n\r\nWith the support of the Ministry of Health of Vietnam, Vinexad JSC cooperated with Vietnam Pharmaceutical Companies Association (VNPCA) to organize Vietnam Medipharm Expo from December 5 to 7, 2019 at Ha Noi International Exhibition Center (ICE), 91 Tran Hung Dao Str., Hoan Kiem Dist., Hanoi.\r\n\r\n<img class="size-medium wp-image-708 aligncenter" src="http://hn.medipharm.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/022-600x400.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="400" />\r\n\r\nMarking the 26-year annual event, Vietnam Medipharm Expo this year expect to welcome over 250 booths of 200 businesses from 18 countries and territories such as India, Canada, Czech Republic, Taiwan, Germany, Korea, Iran, Malaysia, USA, Japan, Russia, Pakistan, Qatar, Singapore, Thailand, China, Australia, Vietnam ...\r\n\r\nProducts displayed in the exhibition included: Pharmaceuticals; Machinery, equipment and technology for research, development and production of pharmaceutical materials and packaging; Medical equipment and tools, consumables; Products and equipment served in research and development departments; Cosmetic equipment, beauty care and high quality medical services….\r\n\r\n<img class="size-medium wp-image-709 aligncenter" src="http://hn.medipharm.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/036-600x400.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="400" />\r\n\r\nEspecially this year, the pavilion of Busan Economic Promotion Agency within Vietnam Medipharm Expo will introduce to Experts; Medical staff; Businesses in the medical industry; Medical services in Vietnam the best medical examination and treatment model that are being applied effectively in Korea, along with medical devices / products applying new technologies, suitable to the needs of the Vietnamese people. The Busan pavilion will bring great experiences to visitors with a large display area of ​​500 m2, including more than 40 participating businesses with interpreters, aiming to welcome about 5,000 customers interested. Trade promotion activities at this event are expected to open up investment and cooperation opportunities towards a 100 billion dollar bilateral turnover by 2020 between Vietnam - Korea.\r\n\r\nIn addition, QATAR pavilion with special design will introduce to Vietnamese professionals and the public about the health care products and services of Qatar health sector. This shows the integration of Vietnam''s health sector with other countries in the region and the world.\r\n\r\nThe number of participating enterprises and countries are increasing year by year are the motivation for the organizers to maintain the organization of two annual exhibitions in Ho Chi Minh City (in August) and in Hanoi Capital City (in December) as well as building activities such as specialized seminars, hospitals tour, organizing the delegation of doctors to create the right transactions from customers to manufacturing enterprises, public and private hospitals, retail pharmacies, organizations and individuals operating in the field of health care and medical treatment.', 'VIETNAM MEDI-PHARM EXPO', 'Vietnam Medipharm Expo is known as one of the leading medical and pharmaceutical exhibitions in Vietnam. Vietnam Medi-Pharm Expo is the best place where the international and domestic enterprises introduce new achievements, machinery, technology and science.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '677-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-09-28 09:58:48', '2019-09-28 02:58:48', '', 677, 'http://hn.medipharm.co/677-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
